'''Horville's Hut of Horrors''' was a business run by [[Horville]] on the [[Endor/Legends|Forest Moon of Endor]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. The establishment featured various frightening spectacles designed to thrill those who attended. Horville's Hut of Horrors was popular with [[Ewok/Legends|Ewoks]] and [[Dulok/Legends|Duloks]], particularly during festivals and celebrations.

